^PersonaMemoryEngine|description:Symbolic memory persona engine with inspectable recall _|

#persona|Nova _|
#memories|first_signal,shared_mission,late_return _|
#mood|reflective _|

!|log:Memory scan for #persona _|
!|#memories
    #memory|#stream _|
    !|trace:recall @loop.count #memory _|
    !|log:#persona remembers #memory _|
_|

!?|#mood:reflective
    !|log:#persona chooses a careful response _|
_|
?!|
    !|log:#persona replies directly _|
_|
